      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a great deal on a dependable ride! This car is in fair condition and has been a reliable companion, showing some honest signs of use but still offering plenty of life for its next owner. It's a fantastic, budget-friendly option for anyone looking for functional transportation with a solid foundation. If you're looking for a practical vehicle that gets the job done, this is the one for you!",
