    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is very dependable; the engine starts up reliably every time, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal use consistent with its age, there are no major cosmetic flaws or mechanical issues to report. It offers a comfortable ride and is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
